                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Fine hand. The script, slender and upright, shows typical
                           paleographic features of the mid-16th century; at the beginning it
                           appears uneven due to the lack of ruling.</seg>
